valworkbench.measures.internal.WCSS
Class WithinClustersSumSquares

java.lang.Object

WCSSFast, WCSSFastA, WCSSGeneric, WCSSGenericA, WCSSHierarchical, WCSSHierarchicalA, WCSSHierarchicalInit, WCSSHierarchicalInitA
public abstract class WithinClustersSumSquares
extends Measure

The WithinClustersSumSquares is the base class for all WCSS measures. A WithinClustersSumSquares Object encapsulates all the informations needed for a measure. These informations include:

  • An InputMeasure object containing all the informations needed to compute the within clusters sum of squares
  • An input Data Matrix
  • A measure vector containing WCSS values
  • A ClusterMatrix object used to load clustering solutions
  • A data header containing data collected in the experiment
  • A matrix of double containing FOM(e, k) values

Version:
1.0
